data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 2102 E George Richie Rd in Longview! This stunning 4-bedroom, 3-bathroom house is a true paradise nestled in a peaceful neighborhood. As you step inside, be prepared to be enchanted by the spacious open floor plan and abundant natural light that floods the living areas. The heart of this home is the beautifully designed kitchen, featuring modern stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage space for all your culinary adventures. Whether you're hosting a dinner party or enjoying a cozy family meal, the dining area provides the perfect ambiance. The master suite is an oasis of tranquility, offering a private retreat from the world. Pamper yourself in the luxurious ensuite bathroom, complete with a relaxing soaking tub and a separate walk-in shower. The additional three bedrooms are spacious and versatile, providing plenty of room for your family, guests, or even a home office or gym. Step outside into your own private sanctuary. The backyard boasts a spacious patio, ideal for entertaining or simply unwinding after a long day. Imagine hosting summer barbecues, and swimming in the gorgeous sparkling pool, or relaxing in the hot tub. Conveniently located, this home offers easy access to schools, call today for a showing!
